{"id":159812,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/澳广-中国宣布利比亚反对派特使将访华/","date":"2011-06-10T10:30:22Z","modified":"2011-06-10T10:30:22Z","title":"澳广 | 中国宣布利比亚反对派特使将访华","content":"<div>\n<p>2011 年 06 月 10 日</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3240515.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/decrease.gif\" alt=\"Decrease\" title=\"Decrease\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3240515.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/standard.gif\" alt=\"Standard\" title=\"Standard\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3240515.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/increase.gif\" alt=\"Increase\" title=\"Increase\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/mailto/mailto-nojs_query.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3240515.htm&#038;presname=/ra\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/email.gif\" alt=\"Email\" title=\"Email\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/printfriendly.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3240515.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/print.gif\" alt=\"Print\" title=\"Print\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3240515.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/favourite.gif\" alt=\"Favourite\" title=\"Favourite\" /></a></p>\n<p>中国外交部亚非司司长陈晓东宣布，利比亚主要反对派的特使将在近期访问北京。</p>\n<p>分析人士称，此举显示，中国正加强和利比亚反对派接触，同时也是利比亚强人卡扎菲一次外交上的挫败。</p>\n<p>陈晓东说，中国准备在不久的将来接待来自利比亚反对派“全国过渡委员会”的代表。他没有说明这位特使到访的确切日期。</p>\n<p>自从利比亚今年2月爆发大规模示威并演变为武装对抗以来，中国一直采取旁观的态度，不过，最近中国加强了说服双方和解的努力。</p>\n<p>上个星期，中国驻利比亚大使张志良会晤了利比亚反对派全国过渡委员会领袖贾利勒，而在8日，中国外长杨洁篪也接见了卡扎菲领导的利比亚政府的外长奥贝迪。</p>\n<p>与此同时，国际社会进一步向利比亚领袖卡扎菲施压，多个西方和阿拉伯国家承诺，向利比亚反对派提供超过11亿美元援助。</p>\n<p>另据报道，联合国人权专家估计，利比亚4个月以来的战斗已导致1万至1万5千人死亡。</p>\n</p></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.radioaustralia.net.au%2Fchinese%2Farticles%2Fs3240515.htm&#038;title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%88%A9%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9A%E5%8F%8D%E5%AF%B9%E6%B4%BE%E7%89%B9%E4%BD%BF%E5%B0%86%E8%AE%BF%E5%8D%8E\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}